mmends harrahs for blackjack as it had the lowest table prices and friendly croupiers. usual story of move anything in the mini bar and you get charged so you can't store anything else in the fridge, there is a walgreens at the bottom of the palazzo where you can get really cheap bottles of water, coke etc. so don't use the mini bar. the fashion show mall across the road has a reasonable food court. the airport for return journey is really naff. the international terminal is tiny and the shuttle bus that takes you to the domestic terminal is only slightly better.	
