d run of $50 free slot play. We were losing i, slowly - didn't matter it was free play after all! - and in fact were down to $0.58 - yep, fifty eight cents.My wife then started winning, including a progressive jackpot. We cashed out at $247 and some cents. On checking our cash when we got back home to our place in Paradise, we were about $80 UP on what we had gone out with - so we had two nights in the Venetian and gret food and drink, and lots of casino play and came home in profit!	
