f you are ahving a treatment you do get use of the spa for the day or you can pay $40 o go in without a treatment - no pool.We have stayed i the Wynn, Bellagio, and MGM, if you are going to pay the price of the Venetian consider the Bellagio first due to its location on the strip and if your not too concerned about being slightly further down the strip then the Wynn is the best hotel in Vegas by far!!	
